{"tid":251431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩：朝鮮已成「東方核強國」及「亞洲火箭霸主」","createTime":"2017-05-21T02:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T04:28:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c42546450aafc749d2c33c99257ccaaa44e71aac","tid":251431,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170521/s00005/9372cf06de38d71f09f1b27c1f6c2449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170521%2Fs00005%2F9372cf06de38d71f09f1b27c1f6c2449.jpg&h=f4338840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝鮮中央通訊社報道，領導人金正恩與「火星-12」彈道導彈的設計者合照後說，朝鮮現時已經成為「東方核強國」及「亞洲火箭霸主」。<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮領導人金正恩昨日（5月20日）在黨中央大樓前，與「火星-12」彈道導彈的設計者合照。金正恩發言時，向使朝鮮成為「東方核強國」及「亞洲火箭霸主」有重大貢獻的人表示祝賀。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩又指，相信及期待導彈研究部門未來可以研究更多高階武器裝備，使任何敵人都不敢侵犯。"},{"pid":"ec462eea7cdf8fb484c9d8d714339974b67ae9e8","tid":251431,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170521/s00005/1495325520850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170521%2Fs00005%2F1495325520850&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=eac55089\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170521%2Fs00005%2F1495325520850&h=e7a93a76\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170521/s00005/1495325520850</a>"},{"pid":"8c169e275994c1001a8101c112b239404f14e19f","tid":251431,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/0bd162d9f2d3572cfac7931c8813632763d0c3cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F-Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6